Heike has been on the self-development path for the last 15+ years. She meditates, does Tai Chi, is highly spiritual, believes in the Universe and has a unique, creative approach to what is called life.

Due to her work with Hypnotherapists and Coaches -as being a client and having them as clients-, who encouraged her to share her gifts with the world, she started to create her own meditations.

She absolutely loves the power of the mind, and the endless possibilities this holds. She is fascinated of how much things can change, when old paradigms are shifted and new ones are installed.

Coming from a not so great background, she knows how important it is to reframe one's mind when one wants to overcome the past, and thrive and grow into a new and better self and therefore future.

Please note: Heike never uses bells in her meditations, as these would negatively affect those who use them for falling asleep, startle them and bring them back into being awake....read more

Hannes loves to share deep breathing, smiles, and sighing. A sigh creates twice as much air flowing into our lungs and a smile helps to create "happy hormones" :)

After suffering from years of anxiety, insomnia and burnout, Hanna began a mission to make the happiness she so desperately wanted a reality.
